permission.label: read your contacts
permission.name: android.permission.READ_CONTACTS
permission.description: Allows the app to read data about your contacts stored on your phone. Apps will also have access to the accounts on your phone that have created contacts. This may include accounts created by apps you have installed. This permission allows apps to save your contact data, and malicious apps may share contact data without your knowledge.

permission.label: modify your contacts
permission.name: android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS
permission.description: Allows the app to modify the data about your contacts stored on your phone. This permission allows apps to delete contact data.

permission.label: Read calendar events and details
permission.name: android.permission.READ_CALENDAR
permission.description: This app can read all calendar events stored on your phone and share or save your calendar data.

permission.label: add or modify calendar events and send email to guests without owners' knowledge
permission.name: android.permission.WRITE_CALENDAR
permission.description: This app can add, remove, or change calendar events on your phone. This app can send messages that may appear to come from calendar owners, or change events without notifying their owners.

permission.label: send and view SMS messages
permission.name: android.permission.SEND_SMS
permission.description: Allows the app to send SMS messages. This may result in unexpected charges. Malicious apps may cost you money by sending messages without your confirmation.

permission.label: receive text messages (SMS)
permission.name: android.permission.RECEIVE_SMS
permission.description: Allows the app to receive and process SMS messages. This means the app could monitor or delete messages sent to your device without showing them to you.

permission.label: read your text messages (SMS or MMS)
permission.name: android.permission.READ_SMS
permission.description: This app can read all SMS (text) messages stored on your phone.

permission.label: receive text messages (WAP)
permission.name: android.permission.RECEIVE_WAP_PUSH
permission.description: Allows the app to receive and process WAP messages. This permission includes the ability to monitor or delete messages sent to you without showing them to you.

permission.label: receive text messages (MMS)
permission.name: android.permission.RECEIVE_MMS
permission.description: Allows the app to receive and process MMS messages. This means the app could monitor or delete messages sent to your device without showing them to you.

permission.label: Forward cell broadcast messages
permission.name: android.permission.BIND_CELL_BROADCAST_SERVICE
permission.description: Allows the app to bind to the cell broadcast module in order to forward cell broadcast messages as they are received. Cell broadcast alerts are delivered in some locations to warn you of emergency situations. Malicious apps may interfere with the performance or operation of your device when an emergency cell broadcast is received.

permission.label: read cell broadcast messages
permission.name: android.permission.READ_CELL_BROADCASTS
permission.description: Allows the app to read cell broadcast messages received by your device. Cell broadcast alerts are delivered in some locations to warn you of emergency situations. Malicious apps may interfere with the performance or operation of your device when an emergency cell broadcast is received.

permission-group.label: Files and media
permission-group.name: android.permission-group.STORAGE
permission-group.description: access photos, media, and files on your device

permission.label: read the contents of your shared storage
permission.name: android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE
permission.description: Allows the app to read the contents of your shared storage.

permission.label: modify or delete the contents of your shared storage
permission.name: android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE
permission.description: Allows the app to write the contents of your shared storage.

permission.label: read locations from your media collection
permission.name: android.permission.ACCESS_MEDIA_LOCATION
permission.description: Allows the app to read locations from your media collection.

permission.label: access precise location only in the foreground
permission.name: android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION
permission.description: This app can get your precise location from location services while the app is in use. Location services for your device must be turned on for the app to get location. This may increase battery usage.

permission.label: access approximate location only in the foreground
permission.name: android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION
permission.description: This app can get your approximate location from location services while the app is in use. Location services for your device must be turned on for the app to get location.

permission.label: access location in the background
permission.name: android.permission.ACCESS_BACKGROUND_LOCATION
permission.description: This app can access location at any time, even while the app is not in use.

permission-group.label: Call logs
permission-group.name: android.permission-group.CALL_LOG
permission-group.description: read and write phone call log

permission.label: access IMS call service
permission.name: android.permission.ACCESS_IMS_CALL_SERVICE
permission.description: Allows the app to use the IMS service to make calls without your intervention.

permission.label: read call log
permission.name: android.permission.READ_CALL_LOG
permission.description: This app can read your call history.

permission.label: write call log
permission.name: android.permission.WRITE_CALL_LOG
permission.description: Allows the app to modify your phone's call log, including data about incoming and outgoing calls. Malicious apps may use this to erase or modify your call log.

permission.label: reroute outgoing calls
permission.name: android.permission.PROCESS_OUTGOING_CALLS
permission.description: Allows the app to see the number being dialed during an outgoing call with the option to redirect the call to a different number or abort the call altogether.

permission.label: read phone status and identity
permission.name: android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE
permission.description: Allows the app to access the phone features of the device. This permission allows the app to determine the phone number and device IDs, whether a call is active, and the remote number connected by a call.

permission.label: read phone numbers
permission.name: android.permission.READ_PHONE_NUMBERS
permission.description: Allows the app to access the phone numbers of the device.

permission.label: directly call phone numbers
permission.name: android.permission.CALL_PHONE
permission.description: Allows the app to call phone numbers without your intervention. This may result in unexpected charges or calls. Note that this doesn't allow the app to call emergency numbers. Malicious apps may cost you money by making calls without your confirmation.

permission.label: add voicemail
permission.name: com.android.voicemail.permission.ADD_VOICEMAIL
permission.description: Allows the app to add messages to your voicemail inbox.

permission.label: make/receive SIP calls
permission.name: android.permission.USE_SIP
permission.description: Allows the app to make and receive SIP calls.

permission.label: answer phone calls
permission.name: android.permission.ANSWER_PHONE_CALLS
permission.description: Allows the app to answer an incoming phone call.

permission.label: route calls through the system
permission.name: android.permission.MANAGE_OWN_CALLS
permission.description: Allows the app to route its calls through the system in order to improve the calling experience.

permission.label: see and control calls through the system.
permission.name: android.permission.CALL_COMPANION_APP
permission.description: Allows the app to see and control ongoing calls on the device. This includes information such as call numbers for calls and the state of the calls.

permission.label: exempt from audio record restrictions
permission.name: android.permission.EXEMPT_FROM_AUDIO_RECORD_RESTRICTIONS
permission.description: Exempt the app from restrictions to record audio.

permission.name: android.permission.ACCEPT_HANDOVER
permission.description: Allows the app to continue a call which was started in another app.
permission.android.label: continue a call from another app

permission.label: record audio
permission.name: android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO
permission.description: This app can record audio using the microphone at any time.

permission.label: recognize physical activity
permission.name: android.permission.ACTIVITY_RECOGNITION
permission.description: This app can recognize your physical activity.

permission.label: take pictures and videos
permission.name: android.permission.CAMERA
permission.description: This app can take pictures and record videos using the camera at any time.

permission.label: Allow an application or service access to system cameras to take pictures and videos
permission.name: android.permission.SYSTEM_CAMERA
permission.description: This privileged or system app can take pictures and record videos using a system camera at any time. Requires the android.permission.CAMERA permission to be held by the app as well

permission.label: Allow an application or service to receive callbacks about camera devices being opened or closed.
permission.name: android.permission.CAMERA_OPEN_CLOSE_LISTENER
permission.description: This app can receive callbacks when any camera device is being opened (by what application) or closed.

permission-group.label: Body sensors
permission-group.name: android.permission-group.SENSORS
permission-group.description: access sensor data about your vital signs

permission.label: access body sensors (like heart rate monitors)
permission.name: android.permission.BODY_SENSORS
permission.description: Allows the app to access data from sensors that monitor your physical condition, such as your heart rate.

permission.label: use fingerprint hardware
permission.name: android.permission.USE_FINGERPRINT
permission.description: Allows the app to use fingerprint hardware for authentication

permission.label: use biometric hardware
permission.name: android.permission.USE_BIOMETRIC
permission.description: Allows the app to use biometric hardware for authentication

permission.label: set an alarm
permission.name: com.android.alarm.permission.SET_ALARM
permission.description: Allows the app to set an alarm in an installed alarm clock app. Some alarm clock apps may not implement this feature.

permission.label: access extra location provider commands
permission.name: android.permission.ACCESS_LOCATION_EXTRA_COMMANDS
permission.description: Allows the app to access extra location provider commands. This may allow the app to interfere with the operation of the GPS or other location sources.

permission.label: have full network access
permission.name: android.permission.INTERNET
permission.description: Allows the app to create network sockets and use custom network protocols. The browser and other applications provide means to send data to the internet, so this permission is not required to send data to the internet.

permission.label: view network connections
permission.name: android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE
permission.description: Allows the app to view information about network connections such as which networks exist and are connected.

permission.label: view Wi-Fi connections
permission.name: android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE
permission.description: Allows the app to view information about Wi-Fi networking, such as whether Wi-Fi is enabled and name of connected Wi-Fi devices.

permission.label: connect and disconnect from Wi-Fi
permission.name: android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE
permission.description: Allows the app to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to device configuration for Wi-Fi networks.

permission.label: pair with Bluetooth devices
permission.name: android.permission.BLUETOOTH
permission.description: Allows the app to view the configuration of the Bluetooth on the phone, and to make and accept connections with paired devices.

permission.label: access Bluetooth settings
permission.name: android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN
permission.description: Allows the app to configure the local Bluetooth phone, and to discover and pair with remote devices.

permission.label: control Near Field Communication
permission.name: android.permission.NFC
permission.description: Allows the app to communicate with Near Field Communication (NFC) tags, cards, and readers.

permission.label: Preferred NFC Payment Service Information
permission.name: android.permission.NFC_PREFERRED_PAYMENT_INFO
permission.description: Allows the app to get preferred nfc payment service information like registered aids and route destination.

permission.label: find accounts on the device
permission.name: android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS
permission.description: Allows the app to get the list of accounts known by the phone. This may include any accounts created by applications you have installed.

permission.label: allow Wi-Fi Multicast reception
permission.name: android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_MULTICAST_STATE
permission.description: Allows the app to receive packets sent to all devices on a Wi-Fi network using multicast addresses, not just your phone. It uses more power than the non-multicast mode.

permission.label: control vibration
permission.name: android.permission.VIBRATE
permission.description: Allows the app to control the vibrator.

permission.label: Allows the app to access the vibrator state.
permission.name: android.permission.ACCESS_VIBRATOR_STATE
permission.description: Allows the app to access the vibrator state.

permission.label: prevent phone from sleeping
permission.name: android.permission.WAKE_LOCK
permission.description: Allows the app to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

permission.label: transmit infrared
permission.name: android.permission.TRANSMIT_IR
permission.description: Allows the app to use the phone's infrared transmitter.

permission.label: change your audio settings
permission.name: android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS
permission.description: Allows the app to modify global audio settings such as volume and which speaker is used for output.

permission.label: disable your screen lock
permission.name: android.permission.DISABLE_KEYGUARD
permission.description: Allows the app to disable the keylock and any associated password security. For example, the phone disables the keylock when receiving an incoming phone call, then re-enables the keylock when the call is finished.

permission.label: request screen lock complexity
permission.name: android.permission.REQUEST_PASSWORD_COMPLEXITY
permission.description: Allows the app to learn the screen lock complexity level (high, medium, low or none), which indicates the possible range of length and type of the screen lock. The app can also suggest to users that they update the screen lock to a certain level but users can freely ignore and navigate away. Note that the screen lock is not stored in plaintext so the app does not know the exact password.

permission.label: retrieve running apps
permission.name: android.permission.GET_TASKS
permission.description: Allows the app to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. This may allow the app to discover information about which applications are used on the device.

permission.label: manage profile and device owners
permission.name: android.permission.MANAGE_PROFILE_AND_DEVICE_OWNERS
permission.description: Allows apps to set the profile owners and the device owner.

permission.label: reorder running apps
permission.name: android.permission.REORDER_TASKS
permission.description: Allows the app to move tasks to the foreground and background. The app may do this without your input.

permission.label: close other apps
permission.name: android.permission.RESTART_PACKAGES
permission.description: Allows the app to end background processes of other apps. This may cause other apps to stop running.

permission.label: close other apps
permission.name: android.permission.KILL_BACKGROUND_PROCESSES
permission.description: Allows the app to end background processes of other apps. This may cause other apps to stop running.

permission.label: This app can appear on top of other apps
permission.name: android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW
permission.description: This app can appear on top of other apps or other parts of the screen. This may interfere with normal app usage and change the way that other apps appear.

permission.label: run in the background
permission.name: android.permission.RUN_IN_BACKGROUND
permission.description: This app can run in the background. This may drain battery faster.

permission.label: use data in the background
permission.name: android.permission.USE_DATA_IN_BACKGROUND
permission.description: This app can use data in the background. This may increase data usage.

permission.label: run in the background
permission.name: android.permission.REQUEST_COMPANION_RUN_IN_BACKGROUND
permission.description: This app can run in the background. This may drain battery faster.

permission.label: use data in the background
permission.name: android.permission.REQUEST_COMPANION_USE_DATA_IN_BACKGROUND
permission.description: This app can use data in the background. This may increase data usage.

permission.label: set wallpaper
permission.name: android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER
permission.description: Allows the app to set the system wallpaper.

permission.label: adjust your wallpaper size
permission.name: android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER_HINTS
permission.description: Allows the app to set the system wallpaper size hints.

permission.label: set time zone
permission.name: android.permission.SET_TIME_ZONE
permission.description: Allows the app to change the phone's time zone.

permission.label: expand/collapse status bar
permission.name: android.permission.EXPAND_STATUS_BAR
permission.description: Allows the app to expand or collapse the status bar.

permission.label: install shortcuts
permission.name: com.android.launcher.permission.INSTALL_SHORTCUT
permission.description: Allows an application to add Homescreen shortcuts without user intervention.

permission.label: uninstall shortcuts
permission.name: com.android.launcher.permission.UNINSTALL_SHORTCUT
permission.description: Allows the application to remove Homescreen shortcuts without user intervention.

permission.label: read sync settings
permission.name: android.permission.READ_SYNC_SETTINGS
permission.description: Allows the app to read the sync settings for an account. For example, this can determine whether the People app is synced with an account.

permission.label: toggle sync on and off
permission.name: android.permission.WRITE_SYNC_SETTINGS
permission.description: Allows an app to modify the sync settings for an account. For example, this can be used to enable sync of the People app with an account.

permission.label: read sync statistics
permission.name: android.permission.READ_SYNC_STATS
permission.description: Allows an app to read the sync stats for an account, including the history of sync events and how much data is synced.

permission.label: modify system settings
permission.name: android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS
permission.description: Allows the app to modify the system's settings data. Malicious apps may corrupt your system's configuration.

permission.label: make app always run
permission.name: android.permission.PERSISTENT_ACTIVITY
permission.description: Allows the app to make parts of itself persistent in memory. This can limit memory available to other apps slowing down the phone.

permission.label: measure app storage space
permission.name: android.permission.GET_PACKAGE_SIZE
permission.description: Allows the app to retrieve its code, data, and cache sizes

permission.label: run at startup
permission.name: android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED
permission.description: Allows the app to have itself started as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the app to slow down the overall phone by always running.

permission.label: send sticky broadcast
permission.name: android.permission.BROADCAST_STICKY
permission.description: Allows the app to send sticky broadcasts, which remain after the broadcast ends. Excessive use may make the phone slow or unstable by causing it to use too much memory.

permission.label: change network connectivity
permission.name: android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE
permission.description: Allows the app to change the state of network connectivity.

permission.label: request install packages
permission.name: android.permission.REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKAGES
permission.description: Allows an application to request installation of packages.

permission.label: request delete packages
permission.name: android.permission.REQUEST_DELETE_PACKAGES
permission.description: Allows an application to request deletion of packages.

permission.label: ask to ignore battery optimizations
permission.name: android.permission.REQUEST_IGNORE_BATTERY_OPTIMIZATIONS
permission.description: Allows an app to ask for permission to ignore battery optimizations for that app.

permission.label: access Do Not Disturb
permission.name: android.permission.ACCESS_NOTIFICATION_POLICY
permission.description: Allows the app to read and write Do Not Disturb configuration.

permission.label: read install sessions
permission.name: android.permission.READ_INSTALL_SESSIONS
permission.description: Allows an application to read install sessions. This allows it to see details about active package installations.

permission.label: bind to carrier services
permission.name: android.permission.BIND_CARRIER_SERVICES
permission.description: Allows the holder to bind to carrier services. Should never be needed for normal apps.

permission.label: start view permission usage
permission.name: android.permission.START_VIEW_PERMISSION_USAGE
permission.description: Allows the holder to start the permission usage for an app. Should never be needed for normal apps.

permission.label: run foreground service
permission.name: android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE
permission.description: Allows the app to make use of foreground services.

permission.label: permlab_protectProcess
permission.name: sprd.permission.PROTECT_PROCESS
permission.description: set process protect status or level, that will keep the protected process running in high priority

permission.label: send MMS
permission.name: com.unisoc.permission.CTA_SEND_MMS
permission.description: Allows the app to send MMS messages. This may result in unexpected charges. Malicious apps may cost you money by sending messages without your confirmation.

permission.label: write SMS
permission.name: com.unisoc.permission.CTA_WRITE_SMS
permission.description: Allows the app to write SMS messages. Malicious apps may use this to modify your sms.

permission.label: delete SMS
permission.name: com.unisoc.permission.CTA_DELETE_SMS
permission.description: Allows the app to delete SMS messages. Malicious apps may use this to erase your sms.

permission.label: write MMS
permission.name: com.unisoc.permission.CTA_WRITE_MMS
permission.description: Allows the app to write MMS messages. Malicious apps may use this to modify your mms.

permission.label: delete MMS
permission.name: com.unisoc.permission.CTA_DELETE_MMS
permission.description: Allows the app to delete MMS messages. Malicious apps may use this to erase your mms.

permission.label: write calllog
permission.name: com.unisoc.permission.CTA_WRITE_CALLLOG
permission.description: Allows the app to write your phone's call log, including data about incoming and outgoing calls. Malicious apps may use this to modify your call log.

permission.label: delete calllog
permission.name: com.unisoc.permission.CTA_DELETE_CALLLOG
permission.description: Allows the app to delete your phone's call log, including data about incoming and outgoing calls. Malicious apps may use this to erase your call log.

permission.label: write contact
permission.name: com.unisoc.permission.CTA_WRITE_CONTACT
permission.description: Allows the app to write the data about your contacts stored on your phone, including the frequency with which you've called, emailed, or communicated in other ways with specific contacts.

permission.label: delete contact
permission.name: com.unisoc.permission.CTA_DELETE_CONTACT
permission.description: Allows the app to delete the data about your contacts stored on your phone, including the frequency with which you've called, emailed, or communicated in other ways with specific contacts.
